<h2 id=3D"POST/customerDetailsRetrievingcustomerdetailsfromGCM-POST/custome=
rDetails">POST /customerDetails</h2>
<p>This endpoint retrieves customer data from GCM and optionally FinCrime A=
PI for the provided CIS key.</p>
